### Update Violation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/violations/PUT_VIOLATION_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Customer did not show up for reservation on 2025-12-15 at 19:00. No call or notification received."
}

### Delete Violation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/violations/PUT_VIOLATION_ID_HERE
